No. 09-956. Robert Doyle, Petitioner v. American Home Products Corporation, et al. 559 U.S. 1086, 130 S. Ct. 2099,

176 L. Ed. 2d 756,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3271. April 19, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
